snippet.textDisplay:
This sufi song is like a prayer to humanity. It has become my daily routine to listen to this.
Umair Jaswal has a very strong voice. I came to know some people hate him may be because he is sometimes very animated. But I love his singing and expressions. 
Ahmed Jahanzeb has a sweet voice. Very good fusion for the two voices and lovely composition by Shuja Haider.
Even my 5 year old son enjoys this song and the music. He has also started reciting it as well.

Love from India
Gurpreet
